title: Nipsey Hussle Interview and More
itunes:title: Nipsey Hussle Interview and More
description:
Wednesday 2/21- Today on the show we had Nipsey Hussle stop by where he spoke about his new album, his relationship with Jay-Z and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to J.J Redick after he used a derogatory term towards Asians and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
